<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
	<title>ACM Hack</title>

	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/auth/images/favicon.png" />

	<style>

	@font-face {
		font-family: 'Open Sans';
		src: url('/auth/css/OpenSans-Regular.ttf');
	}

	body{
		background-color: #F0F0F0;
	}

	.login-box{
		position: absolute;
		height: 200px;
		width: 500px;
		padding: 30px;
		background: #fff;
		box-shadow: 0px 1px 4px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
		top: 50%;
		left: 50%;
		border-radius: 3px;
		-webkit-transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
				transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
	}

	.login-box > *{
		float: left;
	}

	.col-left{
		width: 280px;
		padding-right: 20px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.divide{
		height: 200px;
		width: 1px;
		background: #F0F0F0;
	}

	.col-right{
		width: 170px;
		margin-left: 20px;
	}

	img{
		width: 200px;
		float: left;
		margin-right: 10px;
	}

	span{
		font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
		color: #694873;
		font-size: 25px;
		line-height: 50px;
		float: left;
	}

	a.return{
		letter-spacing: 0px;
		color: #696969;
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: 14px;
		font-family: 'Open Sans';
	}

	a.return:hover{
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	a.fb-btn{
		background: #4c69ba;
		border: 0;
		color: #fff;
		font-family: "Open Sans";
		font-size: 20px;
		font-weight: bold;
		border-radius: 3px;
		border-color: #4c69ba;
		-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    	text-shadow: 0 -1px 0 #354c8c;
    	cursor: pointer;
	    display: inline-block;
	    vertical-align: top;
	    padding: 10px;
	    vertical-align: center;
	    margin: 35px 0;
	    text-decoration: none;
	}

	svg{
		height: 30px;
		width: 30px;
		float: left;
		margin-right: 8px;
	}

	.col-right > *{
		color: #696969;
	}

	.col-right h3{
		font-size: 16px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}
	.col-right p{
		font-size: 12px;
	}

	h3,p{
		font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.logout{
		width: 250px;
		margin: 90px 0 30px 0;
	}

	@media only screen and (max-width: 580px) {

		.login-box{
			width: 60%;
			height: 80%;
			overflow: auto;
		}

		.logout{
			width: auto;
		}

		.col-left{
			width: 100%;
		}

		.col-left > *{
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		.divide{
			display: none;
		}

		.col-right{
			width: 100%;
			margin: 50px 0;
		}

		svg{
			height: 20px;
			width: 20px;
		}

		a.fb-btn{
			font-size: 14px;
			width: 90%;
		}

	}

	</style>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="login-box">
		<div class="col-left">
			<div class="logo">
				<img src="/auth/images/Hack.svg"/>
			</div>
			<div class="logout"><p>You've logged out.</p></div>
			<a href="/" class="return">return to the homepage</a>
		</div>
		<div class="divide"></div>
		<div class="col-right">
			<h3>Why do you guys need my facebook/google info?</h3><br/>
			<p>ACM hack will not have access to any of your privately accessible data; we just need a method of keeping track of HackSchool students.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
